content.rendered:
Directed by Ramkumar

Star Nandita Shwetha (Yazhini). Aryan (Sebastian Chellappa). Meghana Ellen (Bharati Arumugam). Gayathri (Groom’s Mother). Pavan Kumar (Groom). G. Marimuthu (‘Arusuvai’ Arumugam). Raja (Yazhini’s Brother). Sampath Ram (Assistant Commissioner). Madhusudhan Rao (Swamiji). Sindhu Sadhana (Yazhini’s Sister-in-law). Saravana Sakthi (Groom’s Uncle (as Saravana Shakthi)). Sampath (SI Sakthivel). Mahanadhi Shankar (Constable Perumalsamy). Super Subbarayan (Businessman Rajasekaran)

Language Tamil

Producers S Prabhakar

Production Power King Studio
